sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户（Ctrl+C）
    participant REPL as REPL
    participant QE as QueryEngine
    participant Q as query.ts
    participant Tool as BashTool

    User->>REPL: 按 Ctrl+C
    REPL->>QE: interrupt()
    QE->>QE: this.abortController.abort()
    Note over QE: 同一个 AbortController
    QE-->>Q: abortController.signal 触发
    Q-->>Q: 停止流式读取
    Q-->>Tool: 传递 signal，终止 shell 进程
    Q-->>QE: generator 提前结束
    QE-->>REPL: 对话中断
